name: Hookah Life Cigars
description:
Hookah Life Cigars are available in 3 flavours and is an electronic shisha cigarette with an LED tip which glows red when inhaled. 

Its great as a novelty item or as a healthier and viable alternative to smoking a cigarette or shisha / Hookah.

No Tobacco
No Nicotine
No Tar
No Carbon Monoxide
No Harmful Toxins
No Odours
Legal Indoors
Big Smoke Clouds and great flavour
Disposable

Up to 500 puffs** or equivalent to 3 packs of cigarettes

Ingredients: Water, Propylene Glycol, Glycerol and eShisha Club Flavours. Made to UK/EU/US standards.

 Over 18s only

**Please note this estimate is based on moderate use of the unit, if harder/longer puffs are taken then this will affect the estimated number as the battery is made to work harder. Colors may vary.

Please be advised that if we don't receive flavour selections within 2 working days then we will pick and mix your flavour selections
